name: Mountains
description: Mountains have the power to awe and inspire like no other landscape on earth. They remind us of our own insignificance in the world, they are a challenge to take on and they have an aesthetic, timeless perfection which leaves us weak at the knees. I spent much of last year living at high-altitude, waking up to views of the mountains, climbing them and even skiing down them. Now, living in a part of India which is as flat as a pancake, I miss the challenge and the beauty of mountains; I miss the way they make my soul sing.
